      <scopecontent id="aspace_sc">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>Collection consists of slides of paintings, sculpture, and architecture by various artists (1,956 slides), American and European, from ca. 1400-2000.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <arrangement id="aspace_arr1">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The slides are arranged alphabetically be the artists' names. Each artist has a separate folder. Within the folders, the slides are accompanied by any available catalog material and documentation.</p>  
      </arrangement>
